imdb.plot outline: Shababna is a magazine show that aims at covering everything the youth are interested in today, from entertainment news from the UAE, the region and Hollywood, to arts and culture, technology, automotive, fashion, social media trends, inspirational stories and interviews with the region's biggest celebrities, the show is fast paced and truly has something for everyone.
imdb.title: Shababna
plot: _Shababna_ (qv) is a magazine show that aims at covering everything the youth are interested in today, from entertainment news from the UAE, the region and Hollywood, to arts and culture, technology, automotive, fashion, social media trends, inspirational stories and interviews with the region's biggest celebrities, the show is fast paced and truly has something for everyone.
